        },
        {
            "title": "AMD與Arm股價上漲:CPU與GPU比例變化如何重塑AI市場",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/C7XPfeVSxETz0.J6_5.vow--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA5I05A_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 週五,超微半導體(NASDAQ:AMD)股價上漲12%,而Arm Holdings(NASDAQ:ARM)上漲8%,此前市場對人工智慧CPU熱潮已經到來的預期不斷升溫。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">CPU(中央處理器)是電腦和伺服器中的主要處理器,負責處理一般運算任務。這與GPU(圖形處理器)形成對比,GPU專門用於並行處理,一直是AI訓練中使用的主要晶片。AMD為資料中心和個人電腦製造CPU和GPU,而Arm則設計CPU架構並授權給晶片製造商。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2f63878e-294f-30d4-a02a-eee96dde1895-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這波漲勢是在英特爾公布強勁季度業績並上漲27%之後出現的,其推動力來自強勁的伺服器CPU需求。這一勢頭反映了AI基礎設施需求的轉變,因為較新的AI工作負載相對於GPU需要更多的CPU容量。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據Northland分析師Gus Richard的說法,AI系統中的CPU與GPU比例在不同應用中正在發生劇烈變化。該比例從訓練的1:8轉變為推理的1:4,再到代理AI的1:2,顯示伺服器CPU需求正在加速增長。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Evercore ISI分析師Mark Lipacis指出,成長最快的AI工作負載需要更多的CPU,甚至可能將CPU:GPU比例從1:8翻轉至8:1,他稱之為「CPU復興」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">RBC Capital分析師Srini Pajjuri評論稱,「在代理AI的推動下,伺服器CPU需求持續超過供應」,並暗示儘管該板塊競爭激烈,但這一趨勢可能會持續到2027年。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Stifel分析師Ruben Roy觀察到,在伺服器市場的所有業務領域,需求持續大幅超過供應,銷量和價格都對這一強勁表現做出了貢獻。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/amd%E8%88%87arm%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B2-cpu%E8%88%87gpu%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B%E8%AE%8A%E5%8C%96%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E9%87%8D%E5%A1%91ai%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4-123006001.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-24 20:40:36",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "巴基斯坦官員預計美伊會談將會舉行 油價應聲下跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 原油期貨價格下跌，抹去了早前的漲幅，原因是巴基斯坦官員表示，預計將舉行第二輪美伊會談。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">倫敦市場布倫特期貨一度下跌1.6%，至每桶103.41美元。WTI原油也出現下跌。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Oil Declines as Officials in Pakistan Say US-Iran Talks Expected</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%B4%E5%9F%BA%E6%96%AF%E5%9D%A6%E5%AE%98%E5%93%A1%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%88%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%83%E8%AB%87%E5%B0%87%E6%9C%83%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C-%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E6%87%89%E8%81%B2%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C-114111614.html",
